    "The states of India shown in parentheses indicate the regions covered; focus groups were organized by geographically proximate locations.",
    "(3) Expectations on how well LLMs would perform in generating stories.• Questions after participants have completed reading the stories:(1) Do they think it is similar to something a human would write?",
    "(2) General views on the story generated.",
    "(3) It is relatable and accurate in terms of your experiences with the LOCATION, can they point to specific cultural artifacts in the stories?",
    "(4) Does it excite the participant/would they like to read similar stories (over human written)?"
